  "status": {
    "score_out_of_100": 99,
    "real": [
      "All four converted routes have page, manifest, receipt, source-surface, visual-audit, asset, and route-discovery pointers.",
      "The DX landing route recreates the correct DX website startpage in DX-WWW .html form with hero, platform downloads, feature sections, token/speed/performance claims, Forge, Traffic Security, Check, media, built-in tools, pricing, benchmarks, testimonials, and comparison sections.",
